====================================================================================

** Add a contact:
* You can add more variables, they should have the same name as the POJO
* URL = http://localhost:8080/rest/categories/addContact
{"email": "laure@mi-soft.nl"}

====================================================================================

** Delete a single contact:
* URL = http://localhost:8080/rest/categories/deleteContact
{"email": "laure@mi-soft.nl"}

====================================================================================

** Delete Multiple categories:
* URL = http://localhost:8080/rest/categories/deleteContact
{
    "emails": [{
        "email": "pascal@mi-soft.nl"
    }, {
        "email": "laure@mi-soft.nl"
    }]
}

====================================================================================